{
  "texts": [
    "The lack of public acceptance impedes advanced technology from achieving its full potential and practical application (Venkatesh et al., 2012).",
    "Similarly, inappropriate trust compromises the effectiveness of automated systems.",
    "Aligning the public's trust level with the developmental stage of automation represents an ideal scenario.",
    "Thus, it is crucial to investigate the factors that shape trust in automation.",
    "In human-automation trust, viewing trust as an attitude is widely accepted."
  ]
}